parameters:
We have quite a gathering, don't we? Well then, I
wonder if it's about to start soon.

Magical girls, thank you for gathering here. What
I'm about to say is very important, so please
listen carefully.

The fierce battle with the demons has been going
on for many years without showing any signs of
ending. However, there is a reason why the battle
has been evenly matched.

The reason why the battle has been evenly matched
is simply because the true boss of the demons has
not yet been revived. The human and loli-mon
tribes are still unaware of the true power of the
demons.

Yes, there is something that should be announced
here. It is that the Demon King Majin Devil has
been revived!

The Devil has been revived? The boss has appeared?
Where did you hear that?

With this, the preparations on the demon side are
complete. It's only a matter of time before this
Reingarnet and other loli-mon regions are invaded.

What are you saying?! We have to fight! That's
right, we won't lose!

It's pointless because all magical girls will
become food for the demons here.

Kyaa! Demons! This should be within the barrier!
Why?!
What on earth is this...! Who is the Lord...?!

I've been waiting for this moment... the day to
devour you all as a feast... hehehe...

The day when I can thoroughly lick, violate, and
impregnate the small bodies of magical girls and
turn them into breeding grounds... ooooh...
Ah...! Lord Candira... is a demon?!

Wha-?! What is happening here?! Lord-! Who are
you...

Hehehe... Thank you for your hard work in raising
the magical girls... Gilcho's role... ends here.

Mmm... So you are... the infamous magical girl...
Konoha...
Gilcho, this is dangerous! Why did you come?!

It seemed like an important conversation, so I
thought I'd join just in case. I never expected it
to turn out like this! Ugh, there are demons
everywhere!

Interesting... It seems that I have no choice but
to personally corrupt Konoha... I wonder how much
she can endure...?

So, you've been managing this town from the
beginning. In other words, the attack when I
arrived and the operation of the underground
facility, everything...

I am the one recognized by Lord Devil... Plotting
against the town is nothing... Gwehehehehe.

Konoha... you look absolutely delicious... I must
fill you up with my seed...!

You're truly the worst. I'll defeat you and guide
you to that person called Devil!

Tell me, if you say that there is a way to cross
the Flame Zone and revive Devil, then I will go
and settle this.

H-How dare you... Ryuna... That's right... Where
is Hell... Where is Hell! Why isn't she coming to
help me!
Wha...?! What did you say? You know Hell...

Hell, also known as Belzevia, I've actually
already defeated her.

Huh...? B-Belzevia... you say??? That's... absurd!
Unbelievable!

Actually, I managed to make it all the way to the
Astaloth Labyrinth, and he was there in the back,
so I already defeated him.
Now, Candira, it's the end for you. Disappear.

Ah, Gilcho. It seems like everyone else is safe...
They're mostly okay, it seems.

For now, let's discuss it in the strategy room on
the 2nd floor of the \C[2] Guild.\C[0]

Oh... Hell, you're here... Hurry, do something...
My power still isn't stable...

A demon... does not refer to grotesque monsters
like you.

You're useless, unable to even take care of a
single useless magical girl.
W-What are you saying... Hell, you...!

Do you still not know who I am? I am not your
subordinate, Hell. In fact, such a person does not
exist.

I am the Supreme King Belzevia, the overseer of
the Four Heavenly Demons.
Disgusting until the moment of death...

Hey Konoha. I've always been watching your
activities. I never expected you to defeat all the
demons known as the Four Heavenly Kings.

However, as Lord Candira said, our king Devil has
already awakened. Finally, after many years, they
have been resurrected.

Konoha, you are an astonishment to us. Your power
is not to be underestimated, so come all the way
to the Gate of the Ten Thousand Demons. You have
the right to come to the Astalot Maze...

Don't misunderstand. This is not a trap, but an
invitation for dialogue.
It's up to you what you do...

They managed to escape... The other demons... They
somehow withdrew from here... We barely survived.

Ah, Gilcho. I'm glad to see that you're safe. It
seems like the other girls... are mostly okay too.

For now, let's discuss in the strategy room on the
2nd floor of \C[2] Guild\C[0].

You didn't live up to the hype... It's a shame,
but Konoha-kun... this is as far as you go...

However, there was certainly a glimpse of power...
If fully awakened, you would undoubtedly become
our marvel.

Alright... Take them... They will give birth to
strong demons, I suppose.

You didn't live up to the hype... It's a shame,
but Konoha-kun... this is as far as you go...

But why...? Even though you have become a Devil
Witch, why are you siding with humans...?

It's difficult to have you on our side in such a
half-hearted state...

It's a shame, but goodbye... You will spend
eternity devoted to producing demons...
